{"tid":2291143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★圓通速遞員工以每日 500 元人民幣 租借帳號予從事非法行業人士 超過 40 萬用戶資料洩漏","createTime":"2020-11-18T14:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T14:16:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d33af29a3a921a429cc4430414240512c9bfe954","tid":2291143,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:07:36.000Z","msg":"據中國媒體報導，圓通速遞員工以每日 500 元人民幣，租借員工內部帳號予「黑色產業」團夥（即從事非法行業獲利的人士），超過 40 萬用戶資料洩漏，圓通速遞於昨日（17日）發表聲明，指警方於 9 月已拘捕涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據報導，圓通快遞有 5 名員工，以每日 500 元人民幣，租借其公司內部員工帳號予從事非法行業的人士，其後涉案人士被拘捕。圓通快遞昨日在微博發表聲明，指出於今年 7 月底，公司系統監測到有 2 個帳號存在異常查詢，其後調查發現，有員工利用其員工帳號和第三方非法工具竊取運單信息，其後警方於 9 月作出拘捕，圓通快遞表示會完善信息安全監控系統，更好配合相關執法部門，以打擊違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/18/yt-express-information-secruity/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F18%2Fyt-express-information-secruity%2Flife-tech%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5mt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=0200918e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/18/yt-express-information-secruity/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"c2489604670893896ee36b47671eef2ce954dc34","tid":2291143,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9214cc7ae7be625b2e7cfc3e59d4baeeb865908a","tid":2291143,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:08:22.000Z","msg":"淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" c